{"tid":2256870,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"【裝修】家居配色技巧","createTime":"2020-10-24T16:49:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-14T06:15:38.000Z","uid":125261,"like":12,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"e2f063993a977ad7186b57beeda521b4fa3c1011","tid":2256870,"uid":125261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T16:49:09.000Z","msg":"我係遲嫂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n剛剛睇到有個台灣youtube介紹，點樣幫自己家居配色。<br />\n如果有上美術堂，其實用色技巧老師有教。<br />\n<br />\n但人大個左畀番晒美術老師的話，呢個節目都有助提醒大家點樣揀選自己家居既牆色，地板色，傢俬色，同你既擺設既顏色。<br />\n<br />\n一理通馬國明，明白咩叫做和諧色系同對比色系，就可以整到間屋巧令令。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/MZWzS6RaR4M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMZWzS6RaR4M&d=ob16Qiumsg8bXj4Ev1LzLJMONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=81144d96\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/MZWzS6RaR4M</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pzDPzuTjNgI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpzDPzuTjNgI&d=ob16Qiumsg8bXj4Ev1LzLJMONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=3261d989\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pzDPzuTjNgI</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pzDPzuTjNgI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpzDPzuTjNgI&d=ob16Qiumsg8bXj4Ev1LzLJMONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=3261d989\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pzDPzuTjNgI</a>"},{"pid":"dd233fedd2adc01cef00c86f3c8c73db538b79a5","tid":2256870,"uid":125261,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T17:20:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pzDPzuTjNgI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpzDPzuTjNgI&d=ob16Qiumsg8bXj4Ev1LzLJMONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=3261d989\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pzDPzuTjNgI</a><br />\n<br />\n我覺得睇埋呢個，裝修上真係會撞少好多板。"},{"pid":"baa1cb675d2b0dc755aed6a75494d1c761f7ddf7","tid":2256870,"uid":101600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T17:45:28